  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But they hadn't had enough power, Army, the Hungarians overrun them on March 15.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And so all of a sudden, we came-- became Hungarian citizens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In a way, at that time, that-- that was for us a-- a celebration.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because we feared very much of-- about the Ukrainian independence because we knew that this is supported by-- by Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And besides that, we had a bad-- we have a bad history with-- with Ukrainian independence that goes back to Bogdan Khmelnitsky in 1648 and '49 and also to the [INAUDIBLE] era of 1917 where tens of villages were massacred in the-- in the Ukraine when they-- they wanted to become independent from-- from Russia.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So when the Hungarians came in, we were in a very-- a little bit relieved, at least here is a viable government, but it didn't last long.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They, Hungary, became an ally of-- of Germany, and Germany was pressing on them to-- to deal with the-- with the Jewish question, with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So after about five, six months, after the Hungarians occupied this area, [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] they started-- new edicts started coming out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the first one that-- that-- the first laws that they passed was that Jews are not allowed to take part to-- in the lumber industry, to-- to deal with the lumber industry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that hit especially us in the Carpathian, in-- because most of us were-- were sustaining ourselves with that industry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That was the only industry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Of course, the Hungarians grabbed this part, because this is a-- a-- a area that has a lot of lumber, which they didn't have in their own native-- native land.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So that's when it started in '39.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But somehow, we coped with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
